	<LINE>NURSES FOR THE WEST OF SCOTLAND.</LINE>
	<LINE>The object of this association is to provide trained</LINE>
	<LINE>and experienced women of high character as district</LINE>
	<LINE>nurses, to attend the sick poor in their own homes ;</LINE>
